headline: Is Tractor Supply (TSCO) Pricing Reflect Long Term Growth After Mixed Recent Returns?
summary: Wondering if Tractor Supply's current share price lines up with its real worth, or if the market is missing something you can act on. Over the short term the stock has had mixed returns, with a 2.8% gain over the last 7 days, a 1.8% decline over 30 days, a 1.1% gain year to date and a 3.9% decline over the past year, set against longer term returns of 22.7% over 3 years and 78.3% over 5 years.
